name: Simple 1500 Jitsuyou Series Vol. 10: Tarot Uranai
overview: Simple 1500 Jitsuyou Series Vol.10 - Tarot Uranai is the tenth game in the practical 1500 series released for the Playstation One console by D3 Publisher. This time the game let the user to learn about Tarot since it features a complete database about it, the user can also know his today's tarot (about love, work, home, friendship, health, etc) or even his fortune tells.
